tourBios.personal: Dad flew helicopters...Favorite course he's played is Southern Hills...His favorite pro sports teams are the Detroit Lions and Red Wings...Dream foursome would include Byron Nelson, Tiger Woods and Jack Nicklaus...Twitter handle is @dpreston9.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Mackenzie Tour-PGA T was T15th in 2014 at the PC Financial Open.
